**Overall Meaning:**

This verse describes the conduct of a liberated being who has attained true knowledge. After receiving the blessings of their teachers, they move through the world, free from attachments, anger, and excessive desires. Their diet is simple, and they have complete control over their senses. Their life reflects a state of peace, detachment, and wisdom, reflecting the inner transformation they have achieved. 
